title: Can't login with white keycard (and cant read it with usb reader)
body:
# Bug Report

## Problem

Can't log in with keycard, card is detected, but no result 

**UPDATE**: can't read the card with card reader, it seems that keycard is **broken** after creating new account with latest nightly

#### Expected behaviour

Can log in with keycard

Steps to reproduce
1) new keycard with v3 cap installed
2) latest nightly on galaxy s10
3) create an account with keycard
4) logout
5) try to login with keycard
6) no errors, no login, can wait for minutes and just see loader
